<section id="rdb_lexicographicResources">
    <title>Table: <literal>lexicographicResources</literal></title>
    <para>Implements the <olink targetptr="core_lexicographicResource">lexicographicResource</olink>
        data type.</para>

    <bridgehead>Columns</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>id int primary key</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>title varchar(255)</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>uri varchar(255)</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>language varchar(10)</literal></para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead>Comment</bridgehead>
    <para> If the implementation contains only one lexicographic resource, then the
            <literal>lexicographicResource</literal> table <glossterm>may</glossterm> remain
        unimplemented. </para>

